Notification Daemon Nodoka Engine/Theme
***************************************

LICENSE INFORMATION
===================

This package is licensed under GPLv3+. Read COPYING for more details.

SHORT DESCRIPTION
=================

This package contains the nodoka engine for the notification daemon theme.

REQUIRES
========
In order to build you need these two packages:
libsexy
gtk2

In Fedora this means you need to install libsexy-devel package.

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
=========================
./configure --prefix=/usr
make
su
make install

HOW TO ENABLE
=============
Set gconf "/apps/notification-daemon/theme" key to "nodoka".
